Class V – Hot dip galvanizing   
Structural Steelwork;   
Survey of Lifting Appliances and Lifting Gear;" From Data_Standardisation_Report_for_DWSS: "29. Tradesavailable under the Construction Workers Registration Ordinance (Cap 583) but not specified in this form should be entered against \"Others\" in Items 41 to 45of the form.
